Advanced Aerodynamics picks Turned as CFO . Advanced Aerodynamics & Structures Inc said Thursday it had named David Turner , 61 , vice president and chief financial officer of the jet aircraft manufacturing company . Turner , a certified public accountant , is a former senior manager of Ernst & Whinney and a former partner at Arthur Young & Co , both companies now merged as Ernst & Young . Most recently he was vice president of finance and chief financial officer of Taitron Components Inc of Santa Clarita , Calif . , Advanced Aerodynamics said in a prepared statement . 
